               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Cross-examined by</hi> 
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. CLARKSON</hi>. <hi rend="italic">Q.</hi> Were you present at his trial? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> I was—it was proved that he was a weaver by trade—it was stated that he could earn 8<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. or 9<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. a week, and sometimes 14<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.—I do not know whether he is married.</p>
